videos.description: Bryce Williams misses a layup but Kalib Boone rushes in for the rebound and a putback early for Oklahoma State.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Boone powers home a putback for Oklahoma State) 2020/12/5 ESHEET

videos.headline: Boone powers home a putback for Oklahoma State

videos.description: Off Rondel Walker's block, Cade Cunnigham take the ball the other way and fires a slick pass to Bryce Williams for Oklahoma State's go-ahead bucket seconds before halftime.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Cunningham's smooth pass sets up OSU's go-ahead bucket) 2020/12/5 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cunningham's smooth pass sets up OSU's go-ahead bucket

videos.description: Cade Cunningham first tries to set up Bryce Williams with an alley-oop in transition but after the miss Cunningham is able to drain a tough basket while drawing the foul.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Cunningham manages and-1 after missed alley-oop) 2020/12/5 ESHEET

videos.headline: Cunningham manages and-1 after missed alley-oop

videos.description: Cade Cunningham deceives his Oakland defender with a nice behind-the-back move before throwing up a pass to Kalib Boone at the rim for two.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (OSU's Cunningham connects with Boone for big alley-oop) 2020/12/5 ESHEET

videos.headline: OSU's Cunningham connects with Boone for big alley-oop

videos.description: Cade Cunningham takes the ball away from Oakland's offense, goes the other way and throws down a monster slam.
